Package: pubMR
Title: Text Mining Tool for PubMed database in R
Version: 0.0.0.2
Author: Xiaobei Zhou and Lei Cui
Maintainer: Xiaobei Zhou <joe_xiaobei@hotmail.com>
Description: pubMR is an R package designed for text mining of the PubMed database. Additionally, it provide some highly customized metics to evaluate and visualize results for downstream analysis.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.1)
License: GPL (>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    data.table,
    httr,
    RCurl,
    stringr,
    XML,
    tidyr,
    methods
